{"id":188,"ayahs":[{"number":7,"arabic":"كَيْفَ يَكُونُ لِلْمُشْرِكِينَ عَهْدٌ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ وَعِندَ رَسُولِهِۦٓ إِلَّا ٱلَّذِينَ عَٰهَدتُّمْ عِندَ ٱلْمَسْجِدِ ٱلْحَرَامِ ۖ فَمَا ٱسْتَقَٰمُوا۟ لَكُمْ فَٱسْتَقِيمُوا۟ لَهُمْ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ يُحِبُّ ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ","translation":"HOW COULD they who ascribe divinity to aught beside God be granted a covenant by God and His Apostle, unless it be those [of them] with whom you [O believers] have made a covenant in the vicinity of the Inviolable House of Worship? [As for the latter,] so long as they remain true to you, be true to them: for, verily, God loves those who are conscious of Him.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1242.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":7571,"position":1,"arabic":"كَيْفَ","translation":"কেমন করে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7572,"position":2,"arabic":"يَكُونُ","translation":"(বহাল) থাকবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7573,"position":3,"arabic":"لِلْمُشْرِكِينَ","translation":"জন্যে মুশরিকদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7574,"position":4,"arabic":"عَهْدٌ","translation":"চুক্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7575,"position":5,"arabic":"عِندَ","translation":"কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7576,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7577,"position":7,"arabic":"وَعِندَ","translation":"ও কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7578,"position":8,"arabic":"رَسُولِهِۦٓ","translation":"রাসূলের তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7579,"position":9,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7580,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যাদের (সাথে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_007_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":7